    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Line drawings of Phoreiobothrium swaki n. sp. A. Scolex (QM No. G 235021). B. Hooks (USNM No. 1283357). C. Whole worm (QM No. G 235021). D. Terminal, immature proglottid (QM No. G 235021)." ;
