<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242709>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Scanning electron micrographs of Phoreiobothrium swaki n. sp. A. Scolex, small letters indicate locations of Figures 6 D – F. B. Subloculi. C. Pre-hook region and hooks. D. Microtriches on cephalic peduncle. E. Microtriches on proximal bothridal surface. F. Microtriches on distal bothridal surface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242709/files/figure.png" ;
